                                <p>	 <span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: initial;">Most likely, the payment has not being posted by the bank. You are advised to exercise some patience, confirm the payment status with the bank, then contact our support center if you still have issues resolving your payment.</span></p><p>	<strong></strong></p>
