                        <div id="Col-57" class="panel-collapse collapse in">
                            <div class="panel-body " style="white-space: pre-line">
                                <p>	<em style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: initial;">You can get the printed copy of your permit. After your Permit has been approved and you have been notified, </em></p><ul>	<li><em style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: initial;">Log-in to your account area</em></li>	<li><em style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: initial;">Click on "Total Permits"</em></li>	<li><em style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: initial;">Select the Permit to be printed</em></li>	<li><em style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: initial;">Click on Download permit to view and print respectively.</em></li></ul><p>	<em>NOTE: You can print your permit as many times as you desire.</em></p><p>	<em> <br>	</em></p>
