                        <div id="Col-61" class="panel-collapse collapse in">
                            <div class="panel-body " style="white-space: pre-line">
                                <p>	   First, you re-upload document</p><p>	   To upload your document, please log into the LOBP sytem with your Username and Password,</p><ul>	<li><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: initial;">Click on document library and select the document you wish to upload.</span></li>	<li><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: initial;">Please ensure to refresh the page whenever you make any changes.</span></li>	<li><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: initial;">Once you are done uploading the document, click on "applications" to view you pending and rejected application</span></li>	<li><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: initial;">Select the rejected application and click on continue.</span></li>	<li><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: initial;">Make relevant changes if applicable, then click on "resubmit".</span></li></ul>
