                                <p>	     If your application reference cannot be identified, this means it has not been activated for payment.</p><p>	     To activate your payment please ensure you do the following:</p><ul>	<li><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: initial;">Select the bank payment option on the payment page and click continue.</span></li>	<li><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: initial;">Click continue on the payment summary page again</span></li>	<li><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: initial;">Then go to the bank with the reference number for payment.</span></li></ul>
